import React from 'react'
import { connect } from 'react-redux'
import {
  AppBar,
  Toolbar,
  Grid
} from '@material-ui/core'


import { useStyles } from './style'
import logo from '../../assets/img/logo-elecmetal.png'
import logo_small from '../../assets/img/logo-elecmetal_small.png'



const Footer = () => {
  const classes = useStyles()
  
  return (
    <AppBar className={clsx(classes.root)} position="fixed">
      <Toolbar>
        <Grid container className={classes.NavAll}>
          <Grid item xs={4} sm={2}>
            Logo
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={4} sm={2}>
            Idioma
            Metrica
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={4} sm={2}>
            By 
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Toolbar>
    </AppBar>
  )
}

const connected = connect()(Footer)
export { connected as Footer }
